          </mj-text-->
          <mj-text align="left" padding-left="0" padding-right="0" padding-top="5px" font-size="14px" color="#666666" line-height="21px" font-weight="800" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
            Propositional and Predicate Calculus
          </mj-text>
